          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你所办之事，怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀四太爷：是我去至州衙，将四太爷你能得话，说了一遍。那州官即刻升堂，\n将杨忠叫上堂来。言道限他三天，还了咱的银子便罢；如若不然，就将他妹\n子，送来与你能作妾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵哈哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个会办事的州官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他借咱们爷们的脸使么！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乔四亲家上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四亲家",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了师傅命，来此独虎营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四亲家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "里面有人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁呀？\n哦，原来是亲家呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四亲家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可不是嘛！亲家你好吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吓！亲家什么事吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四亲家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我师傅请四太爷，到我们那里饮酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲家你等等，我与你回一声。\n启四太爷：今有玄师傅，请你能到庙里去喝酒，你能是去不去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "即刻就到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗻。\n亲家，四太爷说啦：随后就到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四亲家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请假，你回来也去吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，我去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乔四亲家下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗四虎下，乔四下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
