    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "朱光祖"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离了河间地，来此是临清。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，朱光祖。是我在霸王庄，投了施大人，请假探望师傅病症，且喜师傅病体\n痊愈。是我来至临清，闻听大人在此下马，不免暗地保护便了。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爬山越岭，探听大人虚实。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "念": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "手下",
        "玄空",
        "罗四虎"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（玄空上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄空",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带发修行，结交绿林。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄空",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带发出家入空门，禅堂不喜读经文。爱惜刀枪与拳棒，最爱美貌女佳人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱家，玄空。闻听施不全，在此下马，是我命人去请罗四太爷。等他到来，准\n备行刺赃官，以替绿林英雄报仇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "手下",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四太爷到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗四虎上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四太爷驾到，未曾远迎，面前赎罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！某家来得卤莽，望乞海涵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "柬帖相邀，有何见谕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有施不全，在此下马。今晚三更时分，去至公馆行刺赃官，替绿林英雄报仇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若能杀却赃官，方可消我心头之恨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "玄空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后堂摆宴，与四太爷痛饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此就要叨扰。请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗四虎、玄空同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "手下→玄空",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "玄空→罗四虎",
          "turns": 4
