    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "乔四",
        "施世纶"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（施世纶上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "乔装打扮把贼访，\n不知恶霸在何方？"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本院，施……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（施世纶四下瞧。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "施世纶。只因此处有一恶霸罗四虎，欺压良民，扰害百姓。是我出了行台，暗\n地私访。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（施世纶看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“独虎营”，“独虎营”。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乔四暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！我说你是个干什么的？在此东瞧西看！"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃是个算命的呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是个算命的？你是哪里人呐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是个乡下人呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好好好！你既会算命，我家四太爷正要找个算命看相的呐！你随我在这来，在\n我这小屋坐坐。\n我说伙计们，给这位先生泡茶吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（施世纶下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈，我看此人好似赃官施不全。我在霸王庄，曾看见过他。我哥哥乔三，就\n叫他杀啦！今个碰着我，也是活该！\n正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "世间无有好事，就怕碰见好人。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "施世纶→乔四",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "乔四→施世纶",
          "turns": 2
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 8,
          "唱": 1,
          "白": 8
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.111,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮摇板"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "黄天霸"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、关泰同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。大人出衙私访，你我前去找寻便了。来此已是独虎营，不免进庄观看。\n请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、关泰同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 2,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "乔四",
        "姐丈隆基被你斩",
        "家院与我乱棍打",
        "施世纶",
        "罗四虎"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍同上。〖水底鱼〗。罗四虎上。乔四迎上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四太爷回来啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔噜噜噜噜……"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四太爷，今个又多贪了几盅吧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某吃得倒也爽快！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四太爷，我与你能找了个看相的，给你能看看好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，叫他前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说相面的先生，你这儿来，我们四太爷叫你呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（施世纶上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四太爷在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "跪下，磕头！"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他乃是个乡下人，一旁坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好造化！坐下，坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生与我看上一看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是是是。四太爷，将尊冠升上一升。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗四虎推巾。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四太爷真乃是好贵相："
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天庭饱满地角方，眼如日月放明光。唇红面白多尊贵，日后定作并肩王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四太爷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "日后定有一字并肩王之位。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一字并肩王之位！"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵呵哈哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个看相的先生！来，赏他纹银十两。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗻。\n先生，四太爷赏你十两银子，等你再与你美言几句，你再闹上一份，你看好不\n好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "施世纶",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢多谢！你要好话多讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说四太爷，你当他是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他就是赃官施不全，到咱们这私访来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是他！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗四虎打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赃官呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "赃官吃了熊心胆，\n阎罗殿前乱胡言。\n仇报仇来冤报冤！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姐丈隆基被你斩、家院与我乱棍打、乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四太爷，若将他打死，与你能洞房花烛不利。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依你之见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "以小子之见，将他交给我，把他吊在马棚之内，我拿小修脚刀，慢慢把他剐了，\n看好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与我搭下去！正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天堂有路你不走，地狱无门闯进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗四虎、乔四同下。）"
        }
      ],
