    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "朱光祖"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离了河间地，来此是临清。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，朱光祖。是我在霸王庄，投了施大人，请假探望师傅病症，且喜师傅病体\n痊愈。是我来至临清，闻听大人在此下马，不免暗地保护便了。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爬山越岭，探听大人虚实。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱光祖下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 2,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 8,
      "label": "第八场",
      "characters_present": [
        "黄天霸"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、关泰同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。大人出衙私访，你我前去找寻便了。来此已是独虎营，不免进庄观看。\n请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、关泰同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 2,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 9,
      "label": "第九场",
      "characters_present": [
        "乔四"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（乔四上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒是高粱水，醉人先醉腿。嘴里说胡话，眼睛活见鬼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，乔四的便是。只因我同哥哥乔三，在霸王庄黄大太爷那里当差服役。不料\n黄大太爷，被施不全杀啦，把我哥哥也奏啦！我扉法子，投奔罗四太爷这儿混"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸、关泰同暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到我们这私访来啦！被我看破，对我们四太爷一说，四太爷大怒，叫小子们一\n路乱棍，打死啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸吓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乔四",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你别害怕，他扉有死。是我将他吊在西北犄角马棚里，我拿修脚刀要把他剐喽！\n我剐不了他，你把我先奏喽，就结啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸杀乔四，救施世纶，关泰背施世纶同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "念": 1,
          "白": 2
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 10,
      "label": "第十场",
      "characters_present": [
        "朱光祖",
        "罗四虎",
        "黄天霸"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。四青袍扶罗四虎同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔噜噜噜噜……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。杨忠妹、花轿上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔等回避了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍同闭门，同下。黄天霸、朱光祖同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "美人，你从了某家，你的造化不小！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨忠妹哭。黄天霸上前，打门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何方毛贼，敢在此偷盗！带我看来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗四虎开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人，前来送死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄天霸",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你老爷，四霸天“赛罗成”黄天霸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗四虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀呀呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱光祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老兄弟，还不动手嘛！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄天霸抓罗四虎衣服，罗四虎下，黄天霸、朱光祖同追下。）"
        }
      ],
